Let’s hear it one time for #restorativejustice and @ladcr excellent event yesterday for the first LA DCR capital event supporting social equity in LA. Excellent words from Dr Brown, so much respect for Ethan and the incredible work he does day in and day out, and an enormous amount of respect for Michelle who has stepped into some enormous boots as interim director and filled them all the way up. There is a gap of mistrust to build within any equity community and the LA DCR is taking tremendous strides to bridge that gap by providing resources and support to the equity applicants and operators they serve. Being willing to hear from myself and the applicants shows the amount of care and concern they have for the work they are doing. I am beyond grateful for @daleskyjones & @oaksterdamuniversity for allowing me to be a part of the BLC coaching program and empowering me to help make actual change in the journeys of these applicants! #LADCR #oaksterdamuniveristy #BLC shout out to @sambaba and @waynetay27 for the production

Ok this one is for the ladies… why am I single? Well this is my type. I’m focusing on me and my goals, my business, and my best interest so that I can be the best mommy to my son and boss to my employees, friend, sister, and so forth. Givers have to set boundaries bc takers have none. It’s time we start really talking about these topics because the stronger you are the more likely you are to hear things like “I can’t believe you would take that” “He seems so nice” “You’re to tough for that” when in reality these types of guys see tearing down strong women as a mark of pride (which is sick) ladies be you, do you, and focus on you until someone deserves what you have to give. Text from @psych_today life experience from yours truly and my broken picker #narcissistrelationship #narcassistawareness #womensupportingwomen #womanempowerment drop your thoughts in the comments and if you feel like it’s your fault let me tell you now 1. YOU did not fail 2. YOU are enough 3. Don’t ever let anyone make you feel otherwise 💕💋 if you need to hear it hit the dm’s and if you don’t donate to the women’s scholarship fund so we can create more empowered educated women 💕
